<view class="page">
  <view class="card" wx:if="{{paymentMode === 'mock'}}"><text class="section-title">联调模式</text><text class="muted">当前为虚拟支付，不会真实扣款；不可用于正式营业。</text></view>
  <view class="card table-order-card" wx:if="{{tableContext}}"><view><text class="table-badge">堂食桌码</text><text class="section-title">{{tableContext.tableName}}</text><text class="muted">{{tableContext.areaName ? tableContext.areaName + ' · ' : ''}}{{tableContext.storeName}}</text></view><text class="table-code" wx:if="{{tableContext.tableCode}}">{{tableContext.tableCode}}</text><text class="muted">本单将绑定该桌台；如需换桌，请重新扫描新桌码。</text></view>
  <view class="card" wx:else><text class="section-title">取餐方式</text><view class="fulfillment pickup-only"><button class="active" disabled="{{detailsLocked}}" data-type="PICKUP" bindtap="chooseFulfillment">门店自取<text>做好后凭取餐码领取</text></button></view><text class="muted">堂食请扫描桌牌二维码，系统会自动绑定桌台。</text><text class="muted" wx:if="{{detailsLocked}}">订单已生成，继续支付时将沿用门店自取</text></view>
  <view class="card"><text class="section-title">商品明细</text><view class="line" wx:for="{{cart}}" wx:key="lineKey"><view><text>{{item.name}}</text><text class="muted">{{item.optionSummary || item.skuName || '默认规格'}} × {{item.quantity}}</text></view><text>¥{{item.price * item.quantity / 100}}</text></view><view class="total"><text>合计</text><text class="price">¥{{amount / 100}}</text></view></view>
  <view class="card remark"><text>备注</text><input value="{{remark}}" disabled="{{detailsLocked}}" placeholder="例如少冰、打包分装" maxlength="80" bindinput="setRemark" /><button class="clear-cart" bindtap="clearAllCart">清空购物车</button></view>
  <view class="pay-footer"><view><text>实付</text><text class="price">¥{{amount / 100}}</text></view><button class="primary" loading="{{submitting}}" disabled="{{submitting}}" bindtap="submitOrder">{{submitting ? '处理中' : (orderNo ? '继续支付' : '提交并支付')}}</button></view>
</view>
